<P>
Let's hear it for "The Young Riders." It is an exciting portrayal of life among 
Pony Express riders. Regardless of the ratings games, here's one non-Nielsen 
viewer who'd like to see it kept on the air. 
</P>
<P>
Sarah Palmer, Pasadena 
</P>
