<HEADLINE>
<P>
PLEASANT DISCOVERY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
My wife and I are fortunate in being able to travel frequently, both in the 
United States and internationally. Recently we had the pleasure of flying on 
Cathay Pacific Airways. I cannot praise Cathay Pacific too highly for the 
outstanding in-flight service and the fine food that we encountered on all of 
our trips. This was particularly noteworthy since we were traveling during a 
heavy traffic period and the cabin was fully occupied. The purpose of this 
letter is to share our discovery with your readers. I wish someone had told me 
about Cathay Pacific long before I discovered it for myself. 
</P>
<P>
ROGER H. SCHNAPP 
</P>
<P>
Newport Beach 
