concert. ; Photo, Principal Dennis Doyle would like to lure back to Torrey 
Pines Elementary School at least 20 students who opted for private academies. ; 
Photo, Students at Torrey Pines Elementary School perform at the school's 
winter song concert. BOB GRIESER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
