<P>
THRIFT SHOP BENEFITS 2 SAN PEDRO GROUPS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Beacon House Assn. and the YWCA of the Harbor Area have joined together to 
operate a thrift shop, which will benefit both groups. The B-Y'SE Thrift Shop 
is located on the main level of the YWCA building, at 437 W. 9th St., San 
Pedro, and is open from 9:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. Monday through Friday. Beacon 
House Assn. is an alcoholic recovery center, on Beacon and 10th Street, serving 
more than 80 men. For more information, call 547-2332. 
</P>
