each scored to lead Laguna Hills (4-3-1) in a semifinal of the seventh-place 
bracket. In the seventh-place quarterfinal, Laguna Hills defeated San Gabriel, 
4-1, and was led by Nicole Joliceour's two goals. 
</P>
