<P>
Photo, USD's John Jerome (25) battles Stephen F. Austin center Tim Holloway 
(54) for a rebound during the first half. Photos by DAVID McNEW / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, Stephen F. Austin's Alonzo Crump blocks a shot attempt by USD's 
Randy Thompson in a rare moment of success for SFA. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
