<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski lost $70 when Toby Jug, his $40 win bet, ran 
third in the sixth race and Colway Rally, his $30 win bet in the Bay Meadows 
Handicap that was simulcast, finished second. Bob, who started the meeting with 
a mythical $1,000 bankroll, is now at $875.30. 
</P>
<P>
For today, Bob's bet is a $20 win parlay from Lark's Legacy in the first race 
to Star Cutter in the fifth. 
</P>
<P>
