<P>
Photo, Victorious Olympic Prospect and Alex Solis have a clear lead over Sam 
Who (left) and Laffit Pincay as they race for finish line in the $105,200 
National Sprint Championship Saturday at Hollywood Park. ROBERT DURELL / For 
The Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
