SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA; HOUSING -- SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA; HOUSING PRICES; STANDARD 
OF LIVING; QUALITY OF LIFE; SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA -- INDUSTRY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA121789-0214 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 150113 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 17, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
