<DOCID> 150134 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 17, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Special Section; Part Q; Page 4; Column 2; Foreign Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
