Source: Pacific Telesis 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Ready to Roll 
</P>
<P>
The number of registered vehicles -- cars, trucks, trailers and motorcycles -- 
is expected to keep climbing. 
</P>
<P>
in millions: 
</P>
