<HEADLINE>
<P>
MAN SHOT TO DEATH BY POLICE IDENTIFIED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
WESTMINSTER 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Police have identified the young man fatally shot by police officers Thursday 
night as they hunted for suspects in a drive-by shooting earlier that evening. 
</P>
<P>
Henry Perez Torres Jr., 18, died early Friday at Fountain Valley Regional 
Hospital and Medical Center, Westminster Police Lt. Larry Woessner said 
Saturday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
